These formulas count all Yes “x” entries that have a non‑empty marker in the respective category column, which matches the described requirement. After inserting the formulas we will save the workbook to the output directory, run `recalculate`, reload the file with `data_only=True`, and verify that the four summary cells contain numeric totals (not None). Finally we will submit the output spreadsheet path.
Code:
